{"tid":1393524,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"招人參加區議會選舉 2019/8/1現況報告(自由系FB同離島區 上線了)","createTime":"2019-08-01T06:20:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T13:09:35.000Z","uid":81591,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"1c1faac78f2c962b87f2baf403d5039e81b47709","tid":1393524,"uid":81591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:20:19.000Z","msg":"之前既POST :<br />\n其實有冇人諗過參選區議會? 每次都有好多建制派自動當選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1245169/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1245169/page/1</a><br />\n招人參加區議會選舉 2019/7/16現況報告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1322375/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1322375/page/1</a><br />\n【區選血債票償之三】連登仔組素人出戰平台 銀行絲打東區挑機福建幫<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190724/59852586\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190724%2F59852586&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5wsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=02b9e3cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190724%2F59852586&h=20e533dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190724/59852586</a><br />\n<br />\n現況報告下先<br />\n1)自由系 FB上線啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個PAGE會幫手分享 同埋介紹 參與呢次計劃 各區積極考慮參選人的未來資訊(希望我地咁做可以幫手分辨到 真/假 獨立積極考慮參選人)<br />\n另外都希望可以招募有興趣幫手既人 一齊運作個專頁<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">現在網編團急需要 有創意既 作家 同埋 圖像設計師 進行製作</span></span></strong><br />\n如果有興趣可以搵 TG : @u998397<br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁及follow Instagram專頁:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/hkhifreedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkhifreedom&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5wsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=41cb0485\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/hkhifreedom</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/hkhifreedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhkhifreedom&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5wsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=6082f941\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/hkhifreedom</a><br />\n希望各爸絲打可以幫手<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">讚好和分享</span></span> 比更多人知道各極考慮參選人既故事<br />\n<br />\n2)參選區議會白區行動已經開始左兩個月 <br />\nA.已經同民主動力協調好 <br />\n另外同反自動(譚香文)果面傾緊撞區問題<br />\n注意:大部分分區都已經冇白區 (鄉村地方仲有白區,驚有生命危險)<br />\nB.依家做緊既野係幫助 不同地區的素人新郎新娘提高佢地既曝光率<br />\n令到更多市民可以知道有班年輕人想幫助社區<br />\nC.各新郎新娘亦研究緊政綱 希望可以真正咁幫到個社區<br />\n如果對自己住緊既區有意見想加入政綱<br />\n歡迎可以聯絡下各區ADMIN比D意見 <br />\n因為街坊更熟識果區既問題 所以好有用<br />\n<br />\n而現在繼續招募緊義工 助選團/智囊團/文宣團/網編團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望更多人手 可以令到計劃成功 踢更多保皇黨出區議會<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">新增左離島區</span></strong></span><br />\nTG group如下 :<br />\n請各位有興趣入分區group既朋友搵以下分區admin申請<br />\n總台TG：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/DistrictCouncil2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDistrictCouncil2019&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5wsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=5335fe54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/DistrictCouncil2019</a><br />\n中西區：<br />\n@totallynotparanoid<br />\n灣仔：<br />\n@artytc<br />\n東區：<br />\n@jfthjbnjk<br />\n南區：<br />\n@mak_tszwun <br />\n深水埗：<br />\n@J555000 <br />\n九龍城：<br />\n@happuhappu <br />\n黃大仙：<br />\n@Addoilla<br />\n觀塘：<br />\n@XiJinPing1999<br />\n荃灣：<br />\n@gobacktomars<br />\n屯門：<br />\n@TMgps<br />\n元朗：<br />\n@loseandquit<br />\n北區：<br />\n@alipoooopo<br />\n大埔：<br />\n@edojamie<br />\n西貢：<br />\n@dllmhksar<br />\n沙田：<br />\n@superman9191<br />\n葵青：<br />\n@Passermoon <br />\n離島：<br />\n@pandorahiu<br />\n文宣:<br />\n@u998397"},{"pid":"3d1c87f26aa95839380e503b66f3c02d4fdd1282","tid":1393524,"uid":132627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:21:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c10881c9a4601faba12052a65c34f067b2972d7c","tid":1393524,"uid":265371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,推"},{"pid":"2c3132db541bedbeef99973e7127075cc0a01837","tid":1393524,"uid":239853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:22:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a983d2de4d7d18024d30f066a0f99fc96d41815e","tid":1393524,"uid":128558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:22:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9216550f5b35ddb717f153ee6b8205056adda714","tid":1393524,"uid":169366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:22:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b96871ee07a4ff74f179789aedda3ad7fdaf5db","tid":1393524,"uid":9857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:22:52.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">8.5三罷</code></pre>"},{"pid":"8dcf4fb3ca10823ead8e00f3f95879da0d54307c","tid":1393524,"uid":45416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:24:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2aaed2554c787c84d54b7060b4508667cc92b4e4","tid":1393524,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:26:33.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n查詢自己是否已確認登記選民資格<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fmob%2F&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5wsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=c8cd4818\" target=\"_blank\">https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/</a>"},{"pid":"de024f8a0a850b401b078c3d1ef35b0e09f2c128","tid":1393524,"uid":270428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:27:24.000Z","msg":"［🎶我們一起禱告吧，來到主跟前屈膝跪拜🎶］<br />\n<br />\n從6月起揭開序幕的漫長抗爭路🛤已踞於香港人之間至今已經兩個月，人人疲憊不堪🤕<br />\n<br />\n因此今個星期繼續有一群熱心的基督徒自發起「與神同行」唱詩活動❤️🎶<br />\n希望將詩歌帶到香港的核心&mdash;&mdash;中環「政府山」，呼喚當權者歸回上帝🗣同時驅走黑暗☀️<br />\n<br />\n我們亦會為着過去的721中環及元朗、728上環所發生之事擺上，為着這些實在令人擔心😖，令到社區彌漫一片白色恐怖的事情🌁獻上禱告，在彼端一起守望，祝福香港，祝福社會🙏<br />\n<br />\n希望大家到場支持📣🙆🏻&zwj;♀️<br />\n<br />\nChannel: <a href=\"https://t.me/walkingwithgod\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwalkingwithgod&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5wsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=6935577c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/walkingwithgod</a><br />\n<br />\n日期：03-08-2019<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：19：00至22：00<br />\n         （18：30集合）<br />\n路線：中途途經律政中心<br />\n            及禮賓府公眾活動區<br />\n<br />\n*是次活動正在申請不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n#walkingwithgodhk"},{"pid":"d2dbdebfc8805dd1c869d47efd5e452dfbaca1be","tid":1393524,"uid":121131,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:27:50.000Z","msg":"據小編統計，目前有機會讓建制派自動當選選區如下：<br />\n<br />\nA中西區 2個<br />\nA04山頂 自由黨楊哲安<br />\nA11西營盤 民建聯盧懿杏--&gt;民建聯劉天正<br />\n<br />\nB灣仔區 0個<br />\n<br />\nC東區 0個<br />\n<br />\nD南區 0個<br />\n<br />\nE油尖旺區 0個<br />\n<br />\nF深水埗區 0個<br />\n<br />\nG九龍城區 0個<br />\n<br />\nH黃大仙區 0個<br />\n<br />\nJ觀塘區 3個<br />\nJ07佐敦谷 民建聯顏汶羽<br />\nJ09雙順 符碧珍<br />\nJ26油塘西 呂東孩<br />\n<br />\nK荃灣區 